name: The "Peep Show" Fitted Zip-Up Hoodie
description: Get seriously eyed in this super cozy, zip-up hoodie.  It's warm, but still fitted so you can stay toasty and sexy all at once. After all, why should we be forced to be frumpy, just 'cuz it's 10 below?  100% Cotton. Coming in S-L.

name: The "Peep Show" Heavyweight Zip-Up Hoodie
description: Get seriously eyed in this super cozy, zip-up hoodie.  It's made of heavyweight cotton, so you'll stay nice n' toasty while still looking fly.  100% Cotton. Coming in S-XL.

name: The "Peep Show" Fitted Long Sleeved Tee
description: Get seriously eyed in this super comfy, long-sleeved tee.  It's got some stretch, so it'll fit all of your lovely curves and ya' still won't freeze your nips off.  100% Cotton. Coming in XS-XXL.

name: The"Peep Show" Long-Sleeved Tee
description: Get seriously eyed in this super comfy, long-sleeved tee.  This style has a nice, loose fit so you can layer up during the frigid season and still look fly.  100% Cotton. Coming in XS-XXL.

name: The Heartbreaker Fitted V-Neck Tee in Purple
description: Ugh, the feeling of heartbreak... ::sigh:: quite possibly the worst feeling ever. This tee is a tribute to all those nights spent lying on the floor, crying over some douche bag. #Heartbreaker #Imnevertrustinganyoneagain #emobullshit

name: The "Friday Afernoon Special" Unisex Tank
description:
It's a nostalgia-lover's dream.. all your fave 90's teen icons altogether on one shirt!  Does life get better than this?  Probably not.

We've got everyone from Buffy to Moesha featured on this comfy 100% cotton, white unisex style tank.  It also features a GLBC tag on the back so you'll be sure to rep the brand.  Make sure to grab yours asap... these will be going quick!
100% Cotton. Coming in White XS-2XL.

name: "The Crest" Tank Top
description:
Rock the official Girls Like Boys Clothing crest and pay your tribute!  The emblem features fierce kitties and sexy ladies.... what more could ya' want?!
This 100% cotton tank will surely flatter your frame without having to worry about Cleavage Overload or a Muffin-Top Showdown.  And it's super comfy too!

name: "The Crest" Muscle Tee
description:
Rock the official Girls Like Boys Clothing crest and pay your tribute!  The emblem features fierce kitties and sexy ladies.... what more could ya' want?!

Yeah, girl, show off those guns!  This one's already sleeveless, so you don't have to attack your favorite tee with a pair of scissors in order to stay cool outside.  It's got a nice, loose fit, but is not over-sized.

name: The "High Score" Racerback Tank
description:
This one will bring ya' back to the days when you'd stuff your pockets full of quarters and say prayers at night for the high score...That's right, it's an old skool arcade cabinet, adorned with GLBC logos, of course.  Looks like Girls Like Boys Clothing got the high score after all...

100% cotton, white racerback tank. Sizes XS-L.

name: The "Girls Like Boys X Logo" V-Neck Tee
description:
This 100% classy, I mean, cotton V-neck is soft to the touch.
The GLBX design has just the right amount of flare to give you that self-expressive edge, while still looking sharp!

This particular style tee supports a more masculine look, while still having a slim fit.  No more swimming in all that extra material, it's time to put the scuba gear away!

name: The "Tag My A$$" Boy Shorts in Fuchsia
description:
We all have memories of lifting up our dresses and letting some random drummer sign our undies... no? Just me?  Well, anyway, these sexy lil' stretch boy shorts are mighty comfy and feature our Girls Like Boys Clothing tag on the left cheek. For all those moments when you just grab a sharpie and tag up anywhere.

Coming in Fuchsia/Black, Red/Blue, Gray/Purple and Black/Neon Coral.  Sizes S-XL.

name: The "Close-Shave" Shorts in Black/Neon Blue
description: You'll wanna take it alllll off when you're wearing these.  The print wraps around the hips all sexy-like, to accentuate those gorgeous curves you've got.  Features an old school barbers' blade… a favorite image of American Traditional tattoo artists, probably because they look so ill!  The shorts are super stretchy and ever-so-comfortable…great for chillin' around the house in the heat, or showing off to your booty-call.  Made of 90% Nylon, 10% Spandex.  Coming in Black/Neon Blue and Black/Neon Pink.  One-size-fits-all.

name: The "Miss Saber" Booty Shorts in Red
description: Show off dem cheeks in these red-hot babies!  So comfy and stretchy, you'll wanna dance all over the place.. or do other stuff (tehe). They've also got two machetes printed across the front, just to show off your lethal side.  Made of 90% Nylon, 10% Spandex .  Coming in Red/Black.  One-size-fits-all.
